Translation and Typesetting by Benjiboyo (Me)
Cleaning and by Anubis-sama
Commissioned by Anonymous
And this is the last Rainichi Commission for now. No decensor this time, our client went over budget. Still, thank you once again to our lovely commissioner, and of course to Anubis for such fantastic cleaning.
Next up, something... I am pretty unfamiliar with.
